    </section>
    <section>
        <p><img src="https://i.discogs.com/q_jMPLmdCi0ViGFPzijyCGn9IDIfTpi3-bYsf7ij9xk/rs:fit/g:sm/q:90/h:340/w:340/czM6Ly9kaXNjb2dz/LWRhdGFiYXNlLWlt/YWdlcy9SLTM2NTAy/NTI1LTE3NzEwODAz/NDItODYwNi5qcGVn.jpeg" /></p>
<p>大部分都是輕柔、悅耳的爵士/靈魂樂，作為鼓手出身，這張專輯的鼓點都安排得十分不錯。最大亮點應該是 “When Palestine Is Free”，中間的樂器演奏橋段，管樂器吹奏重複的旋律，隱約地有合成器扭曲的音色。</p>
<hr />
<p>Fav tracks: No Others, Test A Small Area, Anyway, I’m Drowning, When Palestine Is Free</p>
<p>Score: 8.1/10</p>
<p>Release date: 2026-02-13</p>
<p>Labels: Strut</p>
    </section>
