    <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<article>
    <section class="header">
        Posted on February 10, 2026
        
        <br>
        
        Tags: <a title="All pages tagged &#39;2025&#39;." href="/tags/2025.html" rel="tag">2025</a>, <a title="All pages tagged &#39;music&#39;." href="/tags/music.html" rel="tag">music</a>, <a title="All pages tagged &#39;ambient&#39;." href="/tags/ambient.html" rel="tag">ambient</a>, <a title="All pages tagged &#39;minimal techno&#39;." href="/tags/minimal%20techno.html" rel="tag">minimal techno</a>
        
    </section>
    <section>
        <p><img src="https://i.discogs.com/gtsOKzjN3MLyLf5tYWwmsIgfIwWg2FOv_gfteIW6aCY/rs:fit/g:sm/q:90/h:600/w:600/czM6Ly9kaXNjb2dz/LWRhdGFiYXNlLWlt/YWdlcy9SLTM1NTA5/OTAwLTE3NjE5MjE3/NTAtNTc1MS5wbmc.jpeg" /></p>
<p>之前去美國玩被說我聽得都是海生館音樂，可能真的是喔… 在 “That Veil of Yours” 裡， Voice Actor 開頭好像就是在講他去水族館看魚（好像是吧， reverb 太多了聽不太清楚他在唸啥）。緩慢的旋律跟像在耳朵深處搔癢的低頻暗色節奏，慢速的歌曲，隨著時間推進整首歌逐漸地崩解，旋律與音色變得更加豐富而扭曲。真的是很讚。</p>
<hr />
<p>Fav tracks: A Point Most Crucial, Outer Shell, That Veil of Yours, Offshore</p>
<p>Score: 8.2/10</p>
<p>Release date: 2025-10-22</p>
<p>Labels: Modern Love</p>
    </section>
</article>
]]></summary>
